<Window x:Class="HarmonicBrain.UsageWindow"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        Title="Using Harmonic Brain" Height="250" Width="400" WindowStartupLocation="CenterOwner">
    <Grid Margin="10">
        <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontFamily="Open Sans" FontSize="14">
1) Play your audio on your favorite media app.
2) Activate Bilateral Stimulation by pressing the 'On/Off' button.
3) Customize your experience with the 3 different speeds.
4) Deactivate Bilateral Stimulation by pressing the 'On/Off' button again.
        </TextBlock>
    </Grid>
</Window>
